text: According to the Times in 1987, smallpox vaccines triggered the awakening of dormant HIV among recipients, causing the AIDS epidemic.
Official government reports suggest the fully vaccinated will develop AIDS by the end of the year.
Government data shows the fully vaccinated will develop AIDS by the end of February.
A post shared on Facebook claims COVID-19 vaccines can cause HIV to develop due to fragments of HIV being used in the vaccine.
People vaccinated against Covid-19 may be experiencing a form of vaccine-induced acquired immunodeficiency syndrome.
Triple Covid-19 vaccinated people will develop AIDS
